CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FA new approach to dealing with 999
OL,7,Fcalls is freeing up more ambulances so
OL,8,Fthey can be sent to life and death
OL,9,Fsituations faster.
OL,11,FThe aim of the Urgent Community
OL,12,FResponse NWAS Pathway, run by Mersey
OL,13,FCare NHS Foundation Trust, alongside
OL,14,FNWAS, is to get patients the right
OL,15,Fhelp, in the right place, as quickly
OL,16,Fas possible.
OL,18,FSince its launch in November 2025,
OL,19,Fambulance response times have improved
OL,20,Fand there's been a significant
OL,21,Freduction in avoidable hospital visits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
