PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FWhen Sandra Hughes, from Bootle in
OL,7,FLiverpool, fell out of bed and
OL,8,Fcouldn't get up - she called 999.
OL,10,FThe 74-year-old who is on dialysis and
OL,11,Fhas other health problems thought she
OL,12,Fwould have to wait for an ambulance
OL,13,Fand then spend hours in A&E.
OL,15,FBut she got the help she needed - at
OL,16,Fhome and much quicker than she
OL,17,Fexpected - after she was clinically
OL,18,Fassessed suitable to be seen by Two-
OL,19,Fhour Urgent Community Response Team -
OL,20,Fpart of the new pathway.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FSandra said: "It was stressful enough
OL,7,Fthe fact I couldn't get up and I had
OL,8,Fto phone the ambulance to help me.
OL,9,FThere was a four hour wait at the time
OL,10,Fand I thought, 'God I can't sit here
OL,11,Ffor that long' and then I got the
OL,12,Fphone call from this team to come."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
