PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FWhile the most serious, life-
OL,7,Fthreatening emergencies continue to
OL,8,Freceive the fastest ambulance
OL,9,Fresponse, less urgent calls are
OL,10,Freviewed by clinicians and if deemed
OL,11,Fappropriate transferred to the Two-
OL,12,Fhour Urgent Community Response Team
OL,13,Fwho assess and treat them within two
OL,14,Fhours of referral.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FSandra said: "Getting help from the
OL,7,Fteam made a big difference because I
OL,8,Fdidn't have to go to hospital to wait.
OL,9,FThere were three very nice people who
OL,10,Fcame to help. If I'd stayed on the
OL,11,Ffloor any longer I probably wouldn't
OL,12,Fhave been able to help them get me up
OL,13,Fand I probably wouldn't have been able
OL,14,Fto walk."
OL,16,FAfter the fall Sandra received further
OL,17,Fvisits from the team to check on her
OL,18,Fcondition and make sure she had the
OL,19,Fhelp she needed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
