PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FAnna Edwards, an occupational
OL,7,Ftherapist at Mersey Care NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust said: "We're a multi-
OL,9,Fdisciplinary team - just in the
OL,10,Fcommunity not in a hospital setting -
OL,11,Fso we're a team of nurses; advanced
OL,12,Fclinical practitioners; pharmacist
OL,13,Fhealthcare assistants. We can give the
OL,14,Fpatients the care they need or most of
OL,15,Fthe patients the care they need, in
OL,16,Ftheir own home rather than having to
OL,17,Fgo into hospitals ,where we all know
OL,18,Fit's extremely busy at the moment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FJon Price, a Consultant Paramedic for
OL,7,FNWAS, said: " From a patient
OL,8,Fperspective - they're getting care in
OL,9,Fthe right service much quicker than
OL,10,Fthey were before. We're also not
OL,11,Fsending ambulances to Category Three
OL,12,Fincidents as much as we were before so
OL,13,Four ambulances are free for Category
OL,14,FOne and Category Two emergencies and
OL,15,Fwe're reducing avoidable admissions
OL,16,Ffor hospitals across the Cheshire and
OL,17,FMerseyside area. "
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
