PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773173477
OL,3,CNew way of dealing with 999 calls to
OL,4,Censure patients get the right help
OL,6,FSo far more than 5,000 people have
OL,7,Fbeen assessed using this new pathway -
OL,8,Fgetting patients the most appropriate
OL,9,Fcare and keeping ambulances available
OL,10,Ffor those most in need.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
